<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Trifle1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Trifle,</orth> subst. a thing of no moment: <bibl n="shak. ven 1023" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 1023</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 48.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 48, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. son 48.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 48, 2</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 2, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 46</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 170</bibl> <cit><quote>(a small t. of wives).</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.430" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 430</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.2.36" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 2, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.3.26" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 3, 26</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.368" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 368</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.222" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 222</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.222" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 222</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.121" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 121</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.119" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.150" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.9" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 9</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 1.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 2, 213</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 3.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.3.125" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 3, 125</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.11" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3.295" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 295</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.322" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 322</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.2.228" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 228</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 165</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 120</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.88" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 88</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.3.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 3, 92</bibl>. <emph>to make --s of</emph> == to make light of: <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 3, 62</bibl>.<lb />Sometimes == a toy, a pleasing bawble: <cit><quote>some enchanted t. to abuse me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 112</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>knacks, --s, nosegays,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 34</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to fetch me --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.133" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 133</bibl></cit>. cf. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2.165" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 165</bibl> and <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 120</bibl>.
